        <!-- Isi Ulasan -->
        <p class="text-xs text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
          Kodingannya rapi banget, rakit landing page pake Astro + Tailwind v4 hasilnya cepet dan enteng parah. Responsif pas dibuka di mobile, mantap bro jasanya!
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Card 2 -->
    <div class="bg-slate-900 border border-slate-800 p-5 rounded-2xl flex flex-col justify-between">
      <div>
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-3">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <div class="w-9 h-9 rounded-full bg-emerald-600 flex items-center justify-center text-xs font-bold text-white uppercase">
              A
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="text-xs font-bold text-white">Ahmad Fauzi</h4>
              <p class="text-[10px] text-slate-500">12 ulasan</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <!-- SVG Resmi Warna-Warni Google Logo -->
          <svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <path d="M22.56 12.25c0-.78-.07-1.53-.2-2.25H12v4.26h5.92c-.26 1.37-1.04 2.53-2.21 3.31v2.77h3.57c2.08-1.92 3.28-4.74 3.28-8.09z" fill="#4285F4"/>
            <path d="M12 23c2.97 0 5.46-.98 7.28-2.66l-3.57-2.77c-.98.66-2.23 1.06-3.71 1.06-2.86 0-5.29-1.93-6.16-4.53H2.18v2.84C3.99 20.53 7.7 23 12 23z" fill="#34A853"/>
            <path d="M5.84 14.09c-.22-.66-.35-1.36-.35-2.09s.13-1.43.35-2.09V7.06H2.18C1.43 8.55 1 10.22 1 12s.43 3.45 1.18 4.94l3.66-2.85z" fill="#FBBC05"/>
            <path d="M12 5.38c1.62 0 3.06.56 4.21 1.64l3.15-3.15C17.45 2.09 14.97 1 12 1 7.7 1 3.99 3.47 2.18 7.06l3.66 2.85c.87-2.6 3.3-4.53 6.16-4.53z" fill="#EA4335"/>
          </svg>
        </div>

        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-2">
          <div class="flex text-[9px] text-amber-400 gap-0.5">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-star"></i>
            <i class="fa-solid fa-star"></i>
            <i class="fa-solid fa-star"></i>
            <i class="fa-solid fa-star"></i>
            <i class="fa-solid fa-star"></i>
          </div>
          <span class="text-[10px] text-slate-500">Sebutulan lalu</span>
        </div>

        <p class="text-xs text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
          Sangat puas sama komponen accordion FAQ dan modal pop-up nya, transisinya mulus banget gak patah-patah pas dibuka. Klien saya langsung suka kodenya.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</div>`
---

<Layout title="10. Google Review Showcase - Blueprint UI">
  <main
    class="mx-auto max-w-4xl bg-slate-950 px-4 py-12 font-sans text-slate-100"
  >
    <!-- HEADER -->
    <header class="mb-8 border-b border-slate-800 pb-6">
      <div class="mb-2 flex items-center gap-3">
        <span
          class="rounded-md border border-sky-500/30 bg-sky-500/10 px-2 py-0.5 font-mono text-[10px] font-bold text-sky-400"
          >10. MUDAH</span
        >
        <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white">
          Google Business Review Cards
        </h1>
      </div>
      <p class="text-sm text-slate-400">
        Komponen pajangan reputasi bisnis (*social proof*) yang meniru anatomi
        layout kartu ulasan resmi Google Places. Menggunakan struktur flexbox
        simetris dan ikon bintang terstandardisasi.
      </p>
    </header>

    <!-- SECTION 1: Live Preview Playground -->
    <section class="mb-12" aria-labelledby="preview-title">
      <h2
        id="preview-title"
        class="mb-3 text-sm font-semibold tracking-wider text-slate-400 uppercase"
      >
        Live Preview
      </h2>

      <!-- Container Sandbox Box -->
      <div
        class="space-y-6 rounded-2xl border border-slate-800 bg-slate-900/40 p-6 shadow-inner"
      >
        <!-- Live Badge Atas -->
        <div
          class="flex flex-col gap-4 rounded-xl border border-slate-800 bg-slate-900 p-4 sm:flex-row sm:items-center sm:justify-between"
        >
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <div
              class="flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-white text-lg font-black shadow select-none"
            >
              <span
                class="bg-linear-to-r from-blue-500 via-red-500 to-yellow-500 bg-clip-text text-transparent"
                >G</span
              >
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xs font-bold text-white">Studion Space Media</h3>
              <div class="mt-0.5 flex items-center gap-2">
                <span class="text-xs font-black text-amber-400">4.9</span>
                <div class="flex gap-0.5 text-[9px] text-amber-400">
                  <i class="fa-solid fa-star"></i><i class="fa-solid fa-star"
                  ></i><i class="fa-solid fa-star"></i><i
                    class="fa-solid fa-star"></i><i class="fa-solid fa-star"
                  ></i>
                </div>
                <span class="text-[10px] text-slate-500">(89 ulasan)</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <button
            onclick="alert('Membuka form Google Maps Asli...')"
            class="rounded-lg border border-slate-700/50 bg-slate-800 px-3 py-1.5 text-[10px] font-semibold text-white transition-colors hover:bg-slate-700"
          >
            Tulis Ulasan
          </button>
        </div>

        <!-- Live Card Grid bawah -->
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2">
          <!-- Card 1 -->
          <div class="rounded-xl border border-slate-800 bg-slate-900 p-4">
            <div class="mb-2 flex items-center justify-between">
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
                <div
                  class="flex h-8 w-8 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-indigo-600 text-xs font-bold text-white"
                >
                  DM
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h4
                    class="flex items-center gap-1 text-xs font-bold text-white"
                  >
                    Muhamad Dion <i
                      class="fa-solid fa-circle-check text-[9px] text-sky-400"
                    ></i>
                  </h4>
                  <p class="text-[9px] font-medium text-amber-500">
                    Local Guide &bull; 18 ulasan
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <!-- SVG Resmi Warna-Warni Google Logo -->
              <svg
                class="h-3.5 w-3.5"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                fill="none"
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              >
                <path
                  d="M22.56 12.25c0-.78-.07-1.53-.2-2.25H12v4.26h5.92c-.26 1.37-1.04 2.53-2.21 3.31v2.77h3.57c2.08-1.92 3.28-4.74 3.28-8.09z"
                  fill="#4285F4"></path>
                <path
                  d="M12 23c2.97 0 5.46-.98 7.28-2.66l-3.57-2.77c-.98.66-2.23 1.06-3.71 1.06-2.86 0-5.29-1.93-6.16-4.53H2.18v2.84C3.99 20.53 7.7 23 12 23z"
                  fill="#34A853"></path>
                <path
                  d="M5.84 14.09c-.22-.66-.35-1.36-.35-2.09s.13-1.43.35-2.09V7.06H2.18C1.43 8.55 1 10.22 1 12s.43 3.45 1.18 4.94l3.66-2.85z"
                  fill="#FBBC05"></path>
                <path
                  d="M12 5.38c1.62 0 3.06.56 4.21 1.64l3.15-3.15C17.45 2.09 14.97 1 12 1 7.7 1 3.99 3.47 2.18 7.06l3.66 2.85c.87-2.6 3.3-4.53 6.16-4.53z"
                  fill="#EA4335"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="mb-1.5 flex items-center gap-2">
              <div class="flex gap-0.5 text-[8px] text-amber-400">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-star"></i><i class="fa-solid fa-star"
                ></i><i class="fa-solid fa-star"></i><i class="fa-solid fa-star"
                ></i><i class="fa-solid fa-star"></i>
              </div>
              <span class="text-[9px] text-slate-500">3 hari lalu</span>
            </div>
            <p class="text-xs leading-relaxed text-slate-400">
              Fix, kodingan tombol hamburger silang presisi-nya beneran langsung
              lurus di tengah! Gak meleset se-piksel pun. Desainnya rapi.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Card 2 -->
          <div class="rounded-xl border border-slate-800 bg-slate-900 p-4">
            <div class="mb-2 flex items-center justify-between">
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
                <div
                  class="flex h-8 w-8 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-pink-600 text-xs font-bold text-white"
                >
                  R
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h4 class="text-xs font-bold text-white">Rini Handayani</h4>
                  <p class="text-[9px] text-slate-500">4 ulasan</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <!-- SVG Resmi Warna-Warni Google Logo -->
              <svg
                class="h-3.5 w-3.5"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                fill="none"
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              >
                <path
                  d="M22.56 12.25c0-.78-.07-1.53-.2-2.25H12v4.26h5.92c-.26 1.37-1.04 2.53-2.21 3.31v2.77h3.57c2.08-1.92 3.28-4.74 3.28-8.09z"
                  fill="#4285F4"></path>
                <path
                  d="M12 23c2.97 0 5.46-.98 7.28-2.66l-3.57-2.77c-.98.66-2.23 1.06-3.71 1.06-2.86 0-5.29-1.93-6.16-4.53H2.18v2.84C3.99 20.53 7.7 23 12 23z"
                  fill="#34A853"></path>
                <path
                  d="M5.84 14.09c-.22-.66-.35-1.36-.35-2.09s.13-1.43.35-2.09V7.06H2.18C1.43 8.55 1 10.22 1 12s.43 3.45 1.18 4.94l3.66-2.85z"
                  fill="#FBBC05"></path>
                <path
                  d="M12 5.38c1.62 0 3.06.56 4.21 1.64l3.15-3.15C17.45 2.09 14.97 1 12 1 7.7 1 3.99 3.47 2.18 7.06l3.66 2.85c.87-2.6 3.3-4.53 6.16-4.53z"
                  fill="#EA4335"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="mb-1.5 flex items-center gap-2">
              <div class="flex gap-0.5 text-[8px] text-amber-400">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-star"></i><i class="fa-solid fa-star"
                ></i><i class="fa-solid fa-star"></i><i class="fa-solid fa-star"
                ></i><i class="fa-solid fa-star"></i>
              </div>
              <span class="text-[9px] text-slate-500">2 minggu lalu</span>
            </div>
            <p class="text-xs leading-relaxed text-slate-400">
              Sistem collapse accordion FAQ nya lancar bgt pas di-install pnpm
              `@alpinejs/collapse`. Jaraknya lega gak mepet lagi.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- SECTION 2: Code Snippet Block (Siap Salin) -->
    <section class="mb-12" aria-labelledby="code-title">
      <h2
        id="code-title"
        class="mb-3 text-sm font-semibold tracking-wider text-slate-400 uppercase"
      >
        Clean Code (Production Ready)
      </h2>
      <article x-data="codeCopier" class="group relative">
        <button
          @click="copy()"
          :class="copied ? 'bg-emerald-500/20 border-emerald-500/40 text-emerald-400' : 'bg-slate-950/60 border-slate-800 text-slate-400 hover:text-slate-200 hover:bg-slate-900'"
          class="absolute top-3 right-3 z-10 flex items-center gap-2 rounded-lg border px-2.5 py-1.5 text-xs font-medium backdrop-blur-sm transition-all duration-200 active:scale-95"
        >
          <i x-show="!copied" class="fa-regular fa-copy text-sm"></i>
          <i
            x-show="copied"
            class="fa-solid fa-check text-sm text-emerald-400"
            x-cloak></i>
          <span x-text="copied ? 'Copied!' : 'Copy'"></span>
        </button>
        <!-- Kuncian h-100 overflow-auto bawaan standard template sandbox -->
        <pre
          class="h-100 overflow-auto rounded-2xl border border-slate-800 bg-slate-900 p-5 pr-20 font-mono text-xs leading-relaxed text-slate-300"><code>{codeSnippet}</code></pre>
      </article>
    </section>

    <!-- SECTION 3: Dokumentasi & Catatan Teknis -->
    <section aria-labelledby="doc-title">
      <h2
        id="doc-title"
        class="mb-3 text-sm font-semibold tracking-wider text-slate-400 uppercase"
      >
        Dokumentasi Logika
      </h2>
      <article
        class="space-y-4 rounded-2xl border border-slate-800/60 bg-slate-900/50 p-5 text-xs leading-relaxed text-slate-400 md:text-sm"
      >
        <p>
          <strong class="text-slate-200">1. Pewarnaan Font Google Brand:</strong
          > Untuk membuat efek huruf **"G"** menyerupai palet warna resmi Google (Biru,
          Merah, Kuning, Hijau) tanpa menggunakan gambar SVG aset luar, kita mengakalinya
          dengan utility <code class="font-mono text-yellow-400"
            >bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-500 via-red-500 to-yellow-500
            bg-clip-text text-transparent</code
          >.
        </p>
        <p>
          <strong class="text-slate-200"
            >2. Indikator Akun Berbobot (Local Guide Badge):</strong
          > Teks berwarna jingga/amber redup (<code
            class="font-mono text-slate-300">text-amber-500</code
          >) diletakkan di bawah nama akunreviewer untuk memvalidasi bobot
          ulasan di mata psikologi pengunjung, persis seperti algoritma Google
          Maps asli.
        </p>
      </article>
    </section>

    <!-- Tombol Kembali -->
    <footer class="mt-12 border-t border-slate-900 pt-6">
      <a
        href="/"
        class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-xs text-slate-500 transition-colors hover:text-white"
      >
        ← Kembali ke Dashboard Sandbox
      </a>
    </footer>
  </main>
</Layout>

<script define:vars={{ codeSnippet }}>
  document.addEventListener('alpine:init', () => {
    Alpine.data('codeCopier', () => ({
      copied: false,
      codeText: codeSnippet,
      copy() {
        navigator.clipboard.writeText(this.codeText)
        this.copied = true
        setTimeout(() => {
          this.copied = false
        }, 2000)
      },
    }))
  })
</script>
